---
title: Beef Stroganoff with creamy mash and mushrooms
description: Beef stroganoff is a Russian dish that dates back to the mid 19th century. There are many foods that can accompany this meal, and in this recipe, you're treated to a hearty helping of creamy mashed potato.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y23_R15_W32_IE_IECLB14139-2_Main_high-d14f3f9c.jpg
